# PWA Icons

This directory contains PWA icons for BridgeChat.

## Current Icons (SVG)
- icon.svg - Main app icon (scalable)
- icon-maskable.svg - Maskable icon for Android adaptive icons

## Optional: Generate PNG Icons
For maximum compatibility, you can generate PNG versions using:
- https://realfavicongenerator.net
- https://www.pwabuilder.com/imageGenerator
- Figma/Sketch export

Recommended sizes:
- icon-192.png (192x192)
- icon-512.png (512x512)
- icon-maskable-192.png (192x192, with safe area padding)
- icon-maskable-512.png (512x512, with safe area padding)
- badge-72.png (72x72, for notification badges)
